I"#<p><a href="https://github.com/jarun/buku/wiki/System-integration">Wiki</a> &amp; <a href="/buku.htm">man</a>.</p>

<p>Import bookmarks from browsers</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>buku --ai
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Search (regex) - seems to be case insensitive</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>buku -r thing
# behaves like *thing*, will find
# something, things, ect
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Encrypt, decrypt database</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>buku -l
buku -k
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>List last 3 added</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>buku -p -3
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Open bookmark numero 285</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>buku -o 285
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Edit bookmark 285 using geany, comment (that becomes searchable) is possible</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>export EDITOR=geany; buku -w 285
</code></pre></div></div>
